title: Xcode 5.1 Developer Preview 2
description:
--------Xcode 5.1 Developer Preview 2--------

INCLUDES: Xcode 5.1 Developer Preview 2. Files are exactly the way they are as a developer would download it! The Xcode app inside the mounted volume should be codesigned. You can verify this by running "codesign -dvvv /Volumes/Xcode/Xcode51-DP2.app".

**Use this software at your own risk**



Xcode 5.1 Developer Preview 2:
     This is a pre-release version of the complete Xcode developer toolset for Mac, iPhone, iPod touch, and iPad. Please review the Release Notes before installing. Xcode 5.1 Developer Preview 2 requires OS X Mountain Lion or later.



How to use:

1. Mount
2. Copy the XCode application to your Applications folder
3. Enjoy and please help by seeding!


Expect more OS X software from me. Not just other builds of Xcode. --TGivier
